title: Atkinson Cleans Up
description: Gus Atkinson takes his fourth five wicket haul to go with his first innings hundred to take the man of the match spoils as England overcome Sri Lanka by 190 runs at Lords. Simon Hughes and Simon Mann report on a poorly attended fourth day at the home of cricket. Learn more about your ad choices. Visit podcastchoices.com/adchoices
author: Simon Hughes
